00:12:05.250 --> 00:12:09.190
social implications,
social change, or who wins,

00:12:09.190 --> 00:12:12.790
who loses if you
do this, and so on.

00:12:12.790 --> 00:12:15.060
It's just fascinating
to me that you're

00:12:15.060 --> 00:12:19.200
teaching teachers or teaching
kids in elementary school.

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:21.840
And you're, in a sense,
teaching the same thing.

00:12:21.840 --> 00:12:24.300
And you're not really
